    <refsection>
    <title>Remarks</title>

    <variablelist>
    
      <varlistentry>
        <term>Document :</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>The default text colourisation is the Scilab's syntaxe colourisation.</para>
          <para>The <literal>auto-indent</literal> mode indent a line according to Scilab's syntaxe (after a return action).</para>
          <para></para>
        </listitem>
      </varlistentry>
      
      <varlistentry>
        <term>Bugs:</term>
        <listitem>
          <para>You can reported bugs in the Bugzilla <ulink url="http://bugzilla.scilab.org">http://bugzilla.scilab.org</ulink></para>
          <para>There are still a few bugs that we are trying to fixe, details can be found in the given link by filtering entries with the "Editor" element.</para>
          <para></para>
        </listitem>
